134
00:08:30,468 --> 00:08:33,136
- What programme?
- Can I have your autograph?

135
00:08:33,304 --> 00:08:37,015
- You don't want my autograph.
- No, I do. It's for my girlfriend.

136
00:08:37,183 --> 00:08:39,184
