139
00:08:49,111 --> 00:08:51,112
Alvy Singer over here!

140
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,281
It's all right, fellas.

141
00:08:53,449 --> 00:08:56,618
Jesus! What did you do?
Come by way of the Panama Canal?

142
00:08:56,786 --> 00:08:59,955
